ever happen, but it would be so cool. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uswipey.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Swipey</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 95<br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/18/02 2:00 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: useless...?</span><hr size=1> You'd get Rogues bitching about wizards infringing on their territory, no doubt. <br>
